{
 "name": "RPlog_Regroup_and_Reconvene",
 "title": "Regroup and Reconvene",
 "summary": "In a luxury suite aboard the casino-ship Empress of the Stars, the doctor Lynae Cassius receives the Sith Malus to plan their next move against a dangerous, emotionally volatile target. Malus warns that a confrontation could prove problematic given the woman's irrationality at their last encounter, and the pair coolly coordinate logistics and a rendezvous. Lynae names Tatooine -- the target's most visible base of operations -- as the meeting place, stirring conflicted memories in Malus, who once ruled and subjugated that world and will now return on very different terms. With characteristic efficiency, Lynae promises swift communication, and Malus departs to set the plan in motion.",
